dct_title_s: Digital shaded-relief map of the island of Cyprus
dct_description_sm: Cyprus. Geological Survey Department. Makhon ha-ge'ologi (Israel) Companion text: Geological framework of the Levant. Volume I: Cyprus and Syria. Volume II: The Levantine Basin and Israel / Valerie A. Krqasheninnikov; John K. Hall; Francis Hirsch; Chaim Benjamini. Jerusalem: Historical Productions-Hall. 2005. 498 p.and 826 p. South Decimal Degree 34.5333. East Decimal Degree 34.6500. West Decimal Degree 34.5333. Map is Plate X. Universal transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by shading. "Prepared for ICGEM-3, Third International Conference on the Geology of the Eastern Mediterranean, Nicosia, Cyprus, September 23-26, 1998." Printed using gray scale on black background as to resemble a negative photographic image.
